ation. Unit tests can miss incorrect repository reads or terminal-state mapping in the integrated flow.","test_description":"Configure max review rounds in test settings. Seed rounds up to the limit with at least one unresolved MUST-FIX finding in the latest stored findings. Execute the real flow transition to terminal outcome. Assert outcome is ESCALATION (or equivalent), PASS is impossible, and escalation metadata references unresolved MUST-FIX items.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.14,"Integration":0.76,"System":0.06,"Agentic":0.02,"Workflow":0.02}}]}
